scenes.description: Ceres Fauna walks through a forest and finds her mascot, Nemu, sleeping.
Fauna finds a bald Sapling and helps it grow its sprout, then interact with it.
A brief transition showing the empty forest scenery.
Fauna returns and introduces the other members of Hololive English Council.
